title: 'Misleading website description.'
body: 'All 6 pcs are of same colour same design though website description was for multi colour. Very thin. Average quality. Not a good buy.'

title: 'Cleaning dusters.'
body: 'The product is useful in kitchen cleaning as was required.'

title: 'Nit upto mark as shown in pic'
body: 'Quality not as shown in image . Colour was also only brown for all dusters . Display showed multicolored. Fabric is also very average.'

title: 'Poor Quality Product'
body: 'Poor Quality Product. i return it..thanks amazon'

title: 'Old dusters I got... Just got only one color...not happy with the product...'
body: 'Not happy with chapati napkins...very old product given by the seller and only one color I got...Not as shown in the images.... disappointed by this product.... only giving one star...'

title: 'Value for money'
body: It is cheaper than market and the quality is also good. You can go for it without hesitation only problem is I got only 2 colors but it's ok.

title: 'UGLY colour and POOR finish.'
body: 'Colour and quality of finish is so ugly and bad that you cannot put chapatti in them. Useful only as kitchen cleaning cloth.'

title: 'Good'
body: 'Updated to reflection'

title: 'Nice stuff'

title: 'Wow great water absorbency'
body: 'Tired of buying so many towel for kitchen use as wiping cloth. This one came pretty and serves the purpose to the fullest. Very good fabric and decent design. Stitches are sturdy. Quick wet and quick dry. Water absorbing quality is what makes this item a delightful purchase. Five stars'

title: 'Leaves lint on utensils.. not a correct product for wiping'
body: 'Leaves lint on utensils not correct for wiping dishes'

title: 'Was not as expected'

title: 'Friendly fabric for kitchen use..'
body: It serves purpose..good for every kitchen use.. first it came only one colour as some reviews mentioned..i didn't except that..i requested Amazon for various colours as shown in the picture..& as i need to understand.. which colour for what purpose i am keeping..for that i need Colour variations for sure..seller replace the product..but with only two variation..so i am giving four star..
